name: Rustruck
description: Rusting like a relic in a post-modern wasteland, Rustruck is a cyberpunk marvel. With its stack of rusted steel and cybernetically enhanced engine, Rustruck howls across the track like a beast of the old world. Its speed is unmatched, and its agility unparalleled; yet, it never fails to display a nostalgic finesse in its every cornering maneuver. Rustruck is truly the champion of the race track.
